info.name: Colorful UserStyles.org
info.description: This will completely change the appearance of UserStyles.org. Extremely buggy and flawed.
info.additionalInfo: This takes a while to load. Why? Because there are a lot of things in the code that shouldn't be there. Why? Because this is actually just a modded version of Userstyles "Hitchhiker" DARK+CENTERED by Cruto (https://userstyles.org/styles/85708/userstyles-hitchhiker-dark-centered). Because of the original license, if you fix or mod this and post it, you have to cite the original style and keep the license as CC BY-SA - Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike.
